      "id": "PopularPost32049",
      "post_content": "Unlike most cards that make you draw and discard, this guy makes you discard before drawing, which is obviously nice if you have an empty hand (or some madness cards / incarnations / retrace / unearth /flashback / threshold or whatever).  \n  ",
